Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是晴天真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 很适合去海水浴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 你里面穿的是泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 是比基尼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里才是 里面是安全裤？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是泳衣 是三角裤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 三角裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啦 没穿安全裤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 比起三角裤我更在意的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 这个无害的也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是光央的泳衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一眼就知道 真不愧是专业跟踪狂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 光央说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么 难道是指那个时候的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 那个时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是决定要默默地看护着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳兄他什么都没说 我也什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢 我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然明白... 但心里总是郁郁寡欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我事先声明啊 我心里郁郁寡欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是因为对光央还有迷恋什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我担心的是超音波...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会不会太在意光央和琳达学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后处理不好她和光央的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我一点也不喜欢超音波 可以说是讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是她的心情我是可以理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然甩过他一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得她差不多可以考虑一下他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当她用高高在上的姿态对待时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却突然发现是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在香子心里小冈是这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她自己太迟钝了 才会被成熟的姐姐抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以说得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没想到像琳达学姐那样的人出现在光央面前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳达学姐非常优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是谁 见到那种人都会喜欢上她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我也事先声明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢的可是香子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点是不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:03:01.02,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,516)}Accident beach
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2次元君迟到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是在公交站等的 我们应该没弄错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去那边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2次元君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了 我说的可是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公交总站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都会确认下电话留言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定时间都晚了20分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打了好几次电话 还在这附近转了好几圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 电话放在行李包里了 没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你们为什么像坐计程车里那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真有呢 像你们这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不考虑我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 这个给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像刚才被一股热风袭击了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是空调 有点坏坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 小冈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了一些事 要30分钟左右才会到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就在附近的咖啡厅消磨一下时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到了就联系我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个情况 30分钟能到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,70)}你所拨打的用户现在处于电波接受不到...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是没有察觉到她自己在圈外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 别耍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在这附近的吧 我到周围找一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为这样我才讨厌3次元啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这之后还要去柳兄家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳兄也是 为什么偏偏就是今天才回老家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜他所赐 要绕远路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说是因为他老爸出差了 他才趁机回去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时机也太巧合了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们难道是被什么诅咒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 我们要往好的方面想 好的方面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得今天去海水浴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里往里面靠一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家店在半地下收不到信号 我又没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下的信号是乱七八糟的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说为什么你们要像坐计程车那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小冈 你今天穿裙子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 方便换衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且里面直接穿泳衣来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我们出发吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 裙子里面是泳衣啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便一问 千波穿的是水库泳衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 虽然有一瞬间考虑过...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是穿普通的泳衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便一问 千波会不会因为忘记带内裤而伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千波才不会忘记东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在几点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10点30分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超出预计时间2个小时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉今天真不走运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费了很长时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 我要坐副驾驶座咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要问琳达学姐的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在嘴巴涂胶水的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 我们好久不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然万里前阵子见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳泽...不对 光央
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香子你怎么了 说的话这么绕口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没这种事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有超音波 你也来打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是也很久没有见面了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千波你好像有些麻烦吧 发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大多的事你都能处理 所以也不用我操心什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前阵子我听万里说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说你马上就是搬家 下个月开始就一个人生活什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是麻烦到和小柳商量的事 你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说加贺 能把薯条给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这么见外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 刚才的千波对我是不是很冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事哦 很普通哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这样推测的 我觉得是这样 应该是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒不觉得是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就这么不顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从下面那条路出去 是不是会更快？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口还在大前面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 不知道什么时候才能到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如直接回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经来到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算到了海边 雨可能还在下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气预报真不靠谱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我们其中一个是不是被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真笑不出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:12:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是半路撤退比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去卫生间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是幽灵尿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真尿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有个卫生间 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿着泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱 脱 脱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点脱掉~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下3秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 我穿的是那条有害的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七彩泳裤！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 等下 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO！冲刺咯--！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要溺水啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我们到底在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在那边旁观边拍摄 你也下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:13:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈像机不能淋雨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里和加贺真实傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 万里那家伙泳裤下面没有穿安全裤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 我们也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 多田氏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生象征性的东西就要现形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大 2D
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为了我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将摇摆的失物据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是完全构成盗领罪的要件啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 为什么柳兄是老大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 香子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尿出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次骂我笨蛋 我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开动了~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万里的拉面看起来很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来看 冈像机的镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 小冈 你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了 千波的鬼脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看 是贝壳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(634,66)}柳兄来 啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(634,66)}不 我不会吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,66)}说得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺和二次元君真奢侈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就放这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡意来袭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳兄 你在旁边陪我说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果安静下来的话 我有自信我能马上睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那换我来开车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有拿到驾驶证吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗？对我来说实在谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来的时候一直都是你一个人开车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会觉得累啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香子 你真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开车应该还不太熟悉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 放心放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我坐副驾驶座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二次元君到后面躺躺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉困到死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香子驾驶技术不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 从头到尾我都会安全驾驶的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过玩的相当愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然下雨的时候 有想过‘啊完蛋了’
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说都很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和香子一起去海边真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得这是活到现在过得最幸福的夏天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那说的有点夸张了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候去巴塞罗那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下星期 但我想和万里在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是说好了吗 这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你玩的开心 礼物就拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很想和万里在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 不和香子聊聊天的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我醒醒！ 快醒过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不可以！我没想诅咒你严重到这种程度啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！这样不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我想要的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没想这样做啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来救救我！谁来...拜托了！谁来...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我转告他‘加油’
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:40.00,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(282,594)}Walk up call
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,72)}啊 没了没了没了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,72)}我竟然忘记带替换内裤了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,72)}哦呀哦呀 小冈我明明那样帮你确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,72)}还是忘带了吗 是嘛 那太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,72)}这可要留下前科了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,72)}你怎么了2D！傻了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:14.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的哦 都说不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:17.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~你还未察觉到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:20.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,在两三小时前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想挽起你的手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,I do not need for ever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:30.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,I can not believe for ever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:34.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要大声说出的这份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:37.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 已让我如此烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:39.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么~为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:44.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一点都~无法领悟我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:51.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是真的~真的爱恋着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:56.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就不要难为情 也不需要言语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:00.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只需半永久地爱着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:03.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我对五千年后怎么样 不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:10.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能活永久 总有一天要死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:16.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,‘永远爱着我’什么的 我听了一点都不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:24.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,首先在我死之前 你只想着如何爱我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:14.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,違うもう　違ってば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:17.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ　また気づかないのね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:20.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,二三時間の前から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,その腕に触れたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I do not need for ever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:30.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I can not believe for ever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:34.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,叫びたい気持ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:37.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら　困るほどあるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:39.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:44.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっとも 悟ってくれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:51.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,本当に　本当に　私に恋してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:56.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,こそばゆい　言葉はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:00.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,半永久的に愛してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:03.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,五千年後なんて興味はない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:10.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,私エンドレスではないの いつかは死ぬのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:16.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠に愛してるよなんて 言われても嬉しくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:24.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,まずは私を死ぬまで  愛する事だけを考えて
